{
  "video_id": "ygHwQXIlKJI",
  "title": "Stunning buildings made from raw, imperfect materials | Débora Mesa Molina",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12840.0,
      "end_time": 16000.0,
      "text": "Architecture is a profession with many rules,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16400.0,
      "end_time": 18439.0,
      "text": "some written, some not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18480.0,
      "end_time": 21280.0,
      "text": "some relevant and others not."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21320.0,
      "end_time": 24400.0,
      "text": "As architects, we&#39;re constantly gravitating"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24800.0,
      "end_time": 28159.0,
      "text": "between following these rules by the book"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28200.0,
      "end_time": 30560.0,
      "text": "or making a space for imagination --"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30600.0,
      "end_time": 32880.0,
      "text": "for experimentation."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32920.0,
      "end_time": 34440.0,
      "text": "This is a difficult balance."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34480.0,
      "end_time": 36400.0,
      "text": "Especially through architecture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36800.0,
      "end_time": 40879.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re trying to challenge preconceptions and push boundaries and innovate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40920.0,
      "end_time": 45680.0,
      "text": "even if just using what we have around and we overlook all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45720.0,
      "end_time": 48160.0,
      "text": "And this is what I&#39;ve been doing along with my team,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48200.0,
      "end_time": 49440.0,
      "text": "Ensamble Studio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49480.0,
      "end_time": 51559.0,
      "text": "and from our very early works"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51600.0,
      "end_time": 54360.0,
      "text": "that happened in strict historic contexts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54400.0,
      "end_time": 57400.0,
      "text": "like the city of Santiago de Compostela."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57800.0,
      "end_time": 61560.0,
      "text": "Here we built the General Society of Authors and Editors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61600.0,
      "end_time": 63560.0,
      "text": "a cultural building."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63600.0,
      "end_time": 65400.0,
      "text": "And on top of all the regulations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65440.0,
      "end_time": 68440.0,
      "text": "we had to use stone by code"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68480.0,
      "end_time": 70520.0,
      "text": "and our experience was limited,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 70560.0,
      "end_time": 73880.0,
      "text": "but we had incredible references to learn from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 73920.0,
      "end_time": 76400.0,
      "text": "some coming from the city itself"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76440.0,
      "end_time": 79390.0,
      "text": "or from nearby landscapes"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 79800.0,
      "end_time": 80600.0,
      "text": "or other remote places"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 80640.0,
      "end_time": 83360.0,
      "text": "that had impacted our education as architects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 83400.0,
      "end_time": 84960.0,
      "text": "and maybe you recognize here."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 85960.0,
      "end_time": 90559.0,
      "text": "But somehow the finished products that industry made available"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 90600.0,
      "end_time": 94440.0,
      "text": "for us as architects to use in our buildings"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 94480.0,
      "end_time": 95960.0,
      "text": "seemed to have lost their soul."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 96640.0,
      "end_time": 100120.0,
      "text": "And so we decided to go to the nearby quarries"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 100160.0,
      "end_time": 104000.0,
      "text": "to better understand the process that transforms a mountain"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 104400.0,
      "end_time": 107800.0,
      "text": "into a perfectly square tile that you buy from a supplier."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 107840.0,
      "end_time": 111600.0,
      "text": "And we were taken by the monumental scale of the material"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 111640.0,
      "end_time": 113720.0,
      "text": "and the actions to extract it."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 114560.0,
      "end_time": 115760.0,
      "text": "And looking carefully,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 115800.0,
      "end_time": 119320.0,
      "text": "we noticed hundreds of irregular blocks piling up everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 119360.0,
      "end_time": 121760.0,
      "text": "They are the leftovers of an extraction sequence:"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 121800.0,
      "end_time": 123920.0,
      "text": "the ugly parts that nobody wants."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 124680.0,
      "end_time": 126200.0,
      "text": "But we wanted them."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 126240.0,
      "end_time": 128000.0,
      "text": "We were inspired."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 128389.99999999999,
      "end_time": 129638.99999999999,
      "text": "And it was a win-win situation"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 129680.0,
      "end_time": 134480.0,
      "text": "where we could get this residual material of great quality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 134520.0,
      "end_time": 135760.0,
      "text": "doomed to be crushed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 135800.0,
      "end_time": 137200.0,
      "text": "at a very low cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 137920.0,
      "end_time": 141959.0,
      "text": "Now, we had to convince our clients that this was a good idea;"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 142000.0,
      "end_time": 145640.0,
      "text": "but foremost, we had to come up with a design process"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 145680.0,
      "end_time": 148400.0,
      "text": "to reuse these randomly shaped rocks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 148800.0,
      "end_time": 149760.0,
      "text": "and we had not done this before."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 150600.0,
      "end_time": 152600.0,
      "text": "Today everything would be much easier"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 152640.0,
      "end_time": 154559.0,
      "text": "because we would go to the quarry"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 154600.0,
      "end_time": 158400.0,
      "text": "with our smartphones equipped with 3-D scanners"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 158800.0,
      "end_time": 160400.0,
      "text": "and we would document each rock,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 160440.0,
      "end_time": 162640.0,
      "text": "turn that into a digital model --"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 162680.0,
      "end_time": 164880.0,
      "text": "highly engineer the whole process."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 164920.0,
      "end_time": 166559.0,
      "text": "But more than a decade ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 166600.0,
      "end_time": 168880.0,
      "text": "we had to embrace uncertainty"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 168920.0,
      "end_time": 172400.0,
      "text": "and put on our boots, roll up our sleeves"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 172800.0,
      "end_time": 174840.0,
      "text": "and move to the quarry for a hands-on experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 176800.0,
      "end_time": 178640.0,
      "text": "And we also had to become the contractors"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 178680.0,
      "end_time": 183560.0,
      "text": "because we failed at finding somebody willing to share the risk with us."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 185880.0,
      "end_time": 191400.0,
      "text": "Now, luckily, we convinced the quarry team to help us build a few prototypes"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 191800.0,
      "end_time": 193680.0,
      "text": "to resolve some of the technical details."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 193720.0,
      "end_time": 196560.0,
      "text": "And we agreed on a few mock-ups,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 196600.0,
      "end_time": 198790.0,
      "text": "but we got excited,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 198120.0,
      "end_time": 200360.0,
      "text": "and one stone led to another"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 200400.0,
      "end_time": 202240.0,
      "text": "until we succeeded to build"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 202280.0,
      "end_time": 206400.0,
      "text": "an 18-meter-long by eight-meter-high structure"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 207720.0,
      "end_time": 210960.0,
      "text": "that recycled all the amorphous material of the quarry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 211000.0,
      "end_time": 212720.0,
      "text": "just supported by gravity --"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 212760.0,
      "end_time": 215000.0,
      "text": "no mortar and no ties."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 216160.0,
      "end_time": 218280.0,
      "text": "And once built and tested,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 218320.0,
      "end_time": 221720.0,
      "text": "moving it to the final site in the city center"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 221760.0,
      "end_time": 224239.0,
      "text": "to unite it with the rest of the building"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 224280.0,
      "end_time": 225600.0,
      "text": "was a piece of cake,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 225640.0,
      "end_time": 228760.0,
      "text": "because by having isolated uncertainty"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 228800.0,
      "end_time": 232520.0,
      "text": "and managed risk in the controlled environment of the quarry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 232560.0,
      "end_time": 235800.0,
      "text": "we were able to complete the whole building in time"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 235120.0,
      "end_time": 236320.0,
      "text": "and on budget,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 236360.0,
      "end_time": 240400.0,
      "text": "even if using nonconventional means and methods."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 240800.0,
      "end_time": 241600.0,
      "text": "And I still get goosebumps"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 241640.0,
      "end_time": 245119.0,
      "text": "when I see this big chunk of the industrial landscape"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 245160.0,
      "end_time": 246600.0,
      "text": "in the city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 246640.0,
      "end_time": 247959.0,
      "text": "in a building,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 248000.0,
      "end_time": 251720.0,
      "text": "experienced by the visitors and the neighbors."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 252880.0,
      "end_time": 256320.0,
      "text": "This building gave us quite a few headaches,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 256360.0,
      "end_time": 260480.0,
      "text": "and so it could have well been an exception in our work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 260519.0,
      "end_time": 264799.0,
      "text": "but instead it started to inform a modus operandi"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 264840.0,
      "end_time": 267200.0,
      "text": "where every project becomes this opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 267240.0,
      "end_time": 272120.0,
      "text": "to test the limits of a discipline we believe has to be urgently reimagined."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 272760.0,
      "end_time": 274680.0,
      "text": "So what you see here are four homes"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 274720.0,
      "end_time": 278280.0,
      "text": "that we have designed, built and inhabited."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 279400.0,
      "end_time": 282719.0,
      "text": "Four manifestos where we are using the small scale"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 282760.0,
      "end_time": 285159.0,
      "text": "to ask ourselves big questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 285800.0,
      "end_time": 288200.0,
      "text": "And we are trying to discover the architectures"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 288240.0,
      "end_time": 293400.0,
      "text": "that result from unconventional applications of pretty mundane materials"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 293440.0,
      "end_time": 294920.0,
      "text": "and technologies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 294960.0,
      "end_time": 298200.0,
      "text": "like concrete in different forms in the top row,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 298240.0,
      "end_time": 301240.0,
      "text": "or steel and foam in the bottom row."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 301280.0,
      "end_time": 303440.0,
      "text": "Take, for instance, these precast concrete beams."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 303480.0,
      "end_time": 305240.0,
      "text": "You have probably seen them"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 305280.0,
      "end_time": 308880.0,
      "text": "building bridges, highways, water channels --"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 308920.0,
      "end_time": 312440.0,
      "text": "we found them on one of our visits to a precast concrete factory."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 313960.0,
      "end_time": 317919.0,
      "text": "And they might not seem especially homey or beautiful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 317960.0,
      "end_time": 322390.0,
      "text": "but we decided to use them to build our first house."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 322800.0,
      "end_time": 324390.0,
      "text": "And this was an incredible moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 324800.0,
      "end_time": 327479.0,
      "text": "because we got to be architects as always,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 327520.0,
      "end_time": 328799.0,
      "text": "builders once more"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 328840.0,
      "end_time": 332159.0,
      "text": "and, for the first time, we could be our own clients."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 333560.0,
      "end_time": 338960.0,
      "text": "So, here we are trying to figure out how we can take these huge catalogue beams"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 339000.0,
      "end_time": 341200.0,
      "text": "of about 20 tons each"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 341240.0,
      "end_time": 346320.0,
      "text": "and stack them progressively around a courtyard space ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 346360.0,
      "end_time": 348280.0,
      "text": "the heart of the house."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 349400.0,
      "end_time": 353120.0,
      "text": "And due to the dimensions and their material quality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 353160.0,
      "end_time": 357520.0,
      "text": "these big parts are the structure that carry the loads to the ground,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 357560.0,
      "end_time": 359560.0,
      "text": "but they are much more than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 359600.0,
      "end_time": 361520.0,
      "text": "They are the swimming pool;"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 361560.0,
      "end_time": 365440.0,
      "text": "they are the walls that divide interior from exterior;"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 365480.0,
      "end_time": 368160.0,
      "text": "they are the windows that frame the views;"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 368200.0,
      "end_time": 369599.0,
      "text": "they are the finishes;"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 369640.0,
      "end_time": 371800.0,
      "text": "they are the very spirit of this house."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 372640.0,
      "end_time": 375800.0,
      "text": "A house that is for us a laboratory"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 375120.0,
      "end_time": 380960.0,
      "text": "where we are testing how we can use standard elements in nonstandard ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 381000.0,
      "end_time": 384960.0,
      "text": "And we are observing that the results are intriguing."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 385000.0,
      "end_time": 386360.0,
      "text": "And we are learning by doing"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 386400.0,
      "end_time": 390440.0,
      "text": "that prefabrication can be much more than stacking boxes"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 390480.0,
      "end_time": 393840.0,
      "text": "or that heavy parts can be airy and transparent."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 395200.0,
      "end_time": 398800.0,
      "text": "And on top of designing and building this house,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 398120.0,
      "end_time": 399440.0,
      "text": "we get invaluable feedback,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 399480.0,
      "end_time": 402560.0,
      "text": "sharing it with our family and our friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 402600.0,
      "end_time": 404480.0,
      "text": "because this is our life"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 404520.0,
      "end_time": 406159.0,
      "text": "and our work in progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 407600.0,
      "end_time": 412480.0,
      "text": "The lessons that we learn here get translated into other projects"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 412520.0,
      "end_time": 414479.0,
      "text": "and other programs"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 414520.0,
      "end_time": 416599.0,
      "text": "and other scales as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 417800.0,
      "end_time": 419880.0,
      "text": "and they inspire new work."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 419920.0,
      "end_time": 423400.0,
      "text": "Here again we are looking at very standard products:"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 423800.0,
      "end_time": 426840.0,
      "text": "galvanized steel studs that can be easily cut and screwed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 426880.0,
      "end_time": 430159.0,
      "text": "insulating foams, cement boards --"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 430200.0,
      "end_time": 433800.0,
      "text": "all materials that you can find hidden in partition walls"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 433840.0,
      "end_time": 435760.0,
      "text": "and that we are exposing;"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 435800.0,
      "end_time": 439520.0,
      "text": "and we are using them to build a very lightweight construction system"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 439560.0,
      "end_time": 441760.0,
      "text": "that can be built almost by anyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 443400.0,
      "end_time": 446800.0,
      "text": "And we are doing it ourselves with our hands in our shop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 446120.0,
      "end_time": 449280.0,
      "text": "and we are architects. We&#39;re not professional builders"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 449320.0,
      "end_time": 451599.0,
      "text": "but we want to make sure it&#39;s possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 451640.0,
      "end_time": 455800.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s so nice that Antón can move it with his hands"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 455120.0,
      "end_time": 457720.0,
      "text": "and Javier can put it in a container,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 457760.0,
      "end_time": 459320.0,
      "text": "and we can ship it"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 459360.0,
      "end_time": 462560.0,
      "text": "like you would ship your belongings if you were moving abroad ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 462600.0,
      "end_time": 464440.0,
      "text": "which is what we did five years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 464480.0,
      "end_time": 466400.0,
      "text": "We moved our gravity center from Madrid"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 466440.0,
      "end_time": 469400.0,
      "text": "and the house of the concrete beams to Brookline."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 470800.0,
      "end_time": 475200.0,
      "text": "And we found the ugly duckling of a very nice neighborhood:"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 475240.0,
      "end_time": 478800.0,
      "text": "a one-story garage and the only thing we could afford."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 479640.0,
      "end_time": 483159.0,
      "text": "But it was OK because we wanted to transform it into a swan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 483200.0,
      "end_time": 487840.0,
      "text": "installing on top our just-delivered kit of parts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 487880.0,
      "end_time": 492159.0,
      "text": "once more becoming the scientists and the guinea pigs."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 494400.0,
      "end_time": 496560.0,
      "text": "So this is a house that uses some of the cheapest"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 496600.0,
      "end_time": 500200.0,
      "text": "and most normal materials that you can find in the market"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 500240.0,
      "end_time": 503160.0,
      "text": "that applies the ubiquitous four-by-eight modulation"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 503200.0,
      "end_time": 506560.0,
      "text": "that governs the construction industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 506600.0,
      "end_time": 510800.0,
      "text": "And yet a different organization of the spaces"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 510120.0,
      "end_time": 512480.0,
      "text": "and a different assembly of the parts"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 512520.0,
      "end_time": 516000.0,
      "text": "is able to transform an economically built home"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 516390.0,
      "end_time": 518439.0,
      "text": "into a luxurious space."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 520390.0,
      "end_time": 524760.0,
      "text": "And now, we&#39;re dreaming and we&#39;re actively working with developers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 524799.0,
      "end_time": 526000.0,
      "text": "with builders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 526390.0,
      "end_time": 527679.0,
      "text": "with communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 527720.0,
      "end_time": 531240.0,
      "text": "to try to make this a reality for many more homes"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 531280.0,
      "end_time": 532720.0,
      "text": "and many more families."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 534720.0,
      "end_time": 539920.0,
      "text": "And you see, the world around us is an infinite source of inspiration"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 539960.0,
      "end_time": 544200.0,
      "text": "if we are curious enough to see beneath the surface of things."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 544240.0,
      "end_time": 546880.0,
      "text": "Now I&#39;m going to take you to the other side of the moon:"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 546920.0,
      "end_time": 549160.0,
      "text": "to the sublime landscape of Montana,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 550280.0,
      "end_time": 553360.0,
      "text": "where a few years ago we joined Cathy and Peter Halstead"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 553400.0,
      "end_time": 558840.0,
      "text": "to imagine Tippet Rise Art Center on a 10,000-acre working ranch."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 560160.0,
      "end_time": 561839.0,
      "text": "And when we first visited the site,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 561880.0,
      "end_time": 566200.0,
      "text": "we realized that all we knew about what an art center is"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 566240.0,
      "end_time": 569400.0,
      "text": "was absolutely pointless for that client,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 569440.0,
      "end_time": 571800.0,
      "text": "for that community, for that landscape."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 572960.0,
      "end_time": 577320.0,
      "text": "The kind of white-box museum type had no fit here."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 577360.0,
      "end_time": 582840.0,
      "text": "So we decided to explode the center into a constellation of fragments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 582880.0,
      "end_time": 586560.0,
      "text": "of spaces spread across the vast territory"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 586600.0,
      "end_time": 591600.0,
      "text": "that would immerse the visitors into the wilderness of this amazing place."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 592960.0,
      "end_time": 595800.0,
      "text": "So back in the office, we are thinking through making,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 595840.0,
      "end_time": 599120.0,
      "text": "using the land both as support and as material,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 599160.0,
      "end_time": 603400.0,
      "text": "learning from its geological processes of sedimentation, erosion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 603800.0,
      "end_time": 605360.0,
      "text": "fragmentation, crystallization --"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 605400.0,
      "end_time": 607240.0,
      "text": "explosion --"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 607280.0,
      "end_time": 611760.0,
      "text": "to discover architectures that are born from the land,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 611800.0,
      "end_time": 615120.0,
      "text": "that are visceral extensions of the landscape,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 616360.0,
      "end_time": 619360.0,
      "text": "like this bridge that crosses Murphy Canyon."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 620440.0,
      "end_time": 621640.0,
      "text": "Or this fountain."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 622840.0,
      "end_time": 625160.0,
      "text": "Like this space topping a hill ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 626720.0,
      "end_time": 631240.0,
      "text": "or this theatre that brings to us the space of the mountains"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 631280.0,
      "end_time": 632600.0,
      "text": "and its sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 633720.0,
      "end_time": 635480.0,
      "text": "And in order to realize this idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 635520.0,
      "end_time": 638400.0,
      "text": "construction cannot be perfectly planned."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 638440.0,
      "end_time": 642160.0,
      "text": "We need to embrace the drastic weather and the local craft."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 642200.0,
      "end_time": 645840.0,
      "text": "We need to control just those aspects that are critical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 645880.0,
      "end_time": 647600.0,
      "text": "like the structural, the thermal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 647640.0,
      "end_time": 650800.0,
      "text": "the acoustical properties embedded in the form."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 650840.0,
      "end_time": 654960.0,
      "text": "But otherwise, improvisation is welcome and is provoked."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 655000.0,
      "end_time": 657720.0,
      "text": "And the moment of construction is still a moment of design"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 657760.0,
      "end_time": 659120.0,
      "text": "and a moment of celebration"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 659160.0,
      "end_time": 665400.0,
      "text": "where different hands, hearts, minds come together to perform a final dance."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 666160.0,
      "end_time": 669480.0,
      "text": "And the result then cannot be anticipated."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 670160.0,
      "end_time": 671839.0,
      "text": "It comes as a surprise."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 673400.0,
      "end_time": 677599.0,
      "text": "And we unwrap architecture like you would unwrap a birthday gift."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 678560.0,
      "end_time": 680920.0,
      "text": "Architecture isn&#39;t uncovered:"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 680960.0,
      "end_time": 682280.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s discovered."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 683240.0,
      "end_time": 687760.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s extracted from the guts of the earth to build a shelter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 687800.0,
      "end_time": 690400.0,
      "text": "one of the most basic human needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 692800.0,
      "end_time": 695400.0,
      "text": "Architecture, art, landscape,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 695800.0,
      "end_time": 697800.0,
      "text": "archaeology, geology -- all made one."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 700400.0,
      "end_time": 703760.0,
      "text": "And by using the resources at our disposal in radical ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 703800.0,
      "end_time": 706479.0,
      "text": "by making a space for experimentation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 706520.0,
      "end_time": 712199.0,
      "text": "we are able to bring to light architectures that find the beauty latent"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 712240.0,
      "end_time": 715240.0,
      "text": "in the raw and imperfect things that surround us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 716280.0,
      "end_time": 718160.0,
      "text": "that elevate them"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 718200.0,
      "end_time": 721160.0,
      "text": "and let them speak their own language."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 722760.0,
      "end_time": 723960.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 724000.0,
      "end_time": 727280.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}